      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This unit delivers linear power up to its 8,400 RPM redline, facilitated by eight individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned VANOS system. The chassis remains taut with excellent torsional rigidity, and the hydraulic steering rack provides the communicative feedback missing in modern EPS systems. Crucially, the rod bearings and throttle actuators have been addressed, ensuring mechanical longevity. Mated to a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock, this specimen offers a visceral, analog driving experience. Well-maintained and mechanically robust, it\u2019s ready for the canyons.",
